### Integration Test Requests

@host = http://localhost:5000
@api_key = secret

### Create a 'coffee' event
POST {{host}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-KEY: {{api_key}}

{
  "type": "coffee",
  "quality": 8
}

### Create a 'work' event with a specific timestamp (UTC)
POST {{host}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-KEY: {{api_key}}

{
  "type": "work",
  "timestamp": "2026-01-12T09:00:00Z",
  "quality": 5
}

### Create a 'poop' event
POST {{host}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-KEY: {{api_key}}

{
  "type": "poop"
}

### Get timeline for today
# Replace the date with today's date if needed
GET {{host}}/timeline?date=2026-01-12
X-API-KEY: {{api_key}}

### Get all events of type 'coffee'
GET {{host}}/events?type=coffee
X-API-KEY: {{api_key}}

### Get stats for all events
GET {{host}}/stats
X-API-KEY: {{api_key}}
